title: I got riot kayle but not the icon??
body: so uh i haven't received my icon that riot was going to present to us but I got my kayle skin??

replies.body: Gifts are being sent out individually and not all players have received everything yet.  We'll have updates posted on our [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Patience while this is all getting wrapped up!
So it's the 24th and I still don't have the icon
The gifts are still being sent out and you should get everything by 9/23.
ah okay i thought it was through 9/20 , oops
